{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_52_03",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 3話 一緒に立ちたい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_etc-04.m4a",
      "text": "何、これ……凄い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is this… amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-02.m4a",
      "text": "客席の光が広がって……ハートの、形……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The lights in the audience are spreading… into the shape of a heart…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666668892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（よし。客席でペンライトが、順番に点いて……）\n（中心から光が広がって、綺麗なハートの形になった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Alright. The penlights in the audience light up in order…）\n（The light spreads from the center‚ forming a beautiful heart shape.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さんが企画して、ファンの人達にも説明して……）\n（麻奈のために作った、友情の形だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Haruko-san planned it and explained it to the fans…）\n（It’s a symbol of friendship made for Mana.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-02.m4a",
      "text": "私一人のために、こんなに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All this… just for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5514993668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thanks-02.m4a",
      "text": "……最高の、お祝いだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s the best celebration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-04.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう、私、本当に今日は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do… today‚ I really…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8355731964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなに感謝を届けたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "want to show my gratitude to all the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6744425892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "楽しんで、笑顔になってもらえたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they enjoy themselves and smile‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1396484056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sigh-01.m4a",
      "text": "それで大満足のはずだったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought that would be enough…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5316900887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……っ、言葉にならないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m at a loss for words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9770640688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-04.m4a",
      "text": "この胸一杯に広がるあったかい気持ち……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This warm feeling spreading throughout my heart…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9999848682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "これから先、私は何度も誕生日を迎えるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ I’ll have many more birthdays‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9878218329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-04.m4a",
      "text": "今日のこの光を、一生忘れないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll never forget the light from today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7834886637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.4385677014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "……はー。みんなのせいで泣いちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Haaー I cried because of everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5052348767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thanks-02.m4a",
      "text": "本当にありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7666617074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.2093192889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-04.m4a",
      "text": "この胸の想いを、今度は私が、みんなに届けるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This feeling in my heart… now it’s my turn to deliver it to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2093192889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私の新曲……特別な、この日のための曲を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My new song… a special song for this day‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3446787506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日という日を、一緒に迎えてくれたみんなへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for everyone who’s celebrating this day with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0200533068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_rep-05.m4a",
      "text": "聴いて下さい――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please listen—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2666591642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4899.996948200012,
          "startTime": 111.1666561124
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.499985377
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.499985377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4108095005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すっごく、いいライブだった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was such a good live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.50000267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、麻奈\n最高に盛り上がったな。楽しんでもらえたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ Mana.\nIt was amazing. Did you have fun?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9999899545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.3180497482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}くん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-kun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3180497482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-05.m4a",
      "text": "も～～、なんだったの、さっきのサプライズ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey～～ what was that surprise earlier!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8332712486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.3354478196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-04.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私、ステージで泣いちゃうなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I ended up crying on stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3354478196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あんなに胸が一杯になるなんて、思わなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t expect my heart to feel so full.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7405082455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-09.m4a",
      "text": "会場がふっと暗くなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The venue suddenly went dark‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.0595245358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "目の前で、光が綺麗に広がっていって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and the light spread beautifully right before my eyes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5333039601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.076922607
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "思い出しただけで、胸が締めつけられるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just remembering it makes my chest tighten.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.076922607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thanks-04.m4a",
      "text": "一生忘れられない思い出になった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It became a memory I’ll never forget…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.033295822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
